          "type": "text",
          "name": "t:names.text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>You might be wondering what those giant bags are that fit 8 boards? They’re team-only customs made for our elite crew who regularly travel with huge quivers. For 99% of surfers, a Multi Tour, Quad or Triple is plenty. </p><p>For this epic week-long strike mission, we also sent over two Doubles, a few Day Use bags, and a bunch of Aerolite board socks, which are a major team favourite.</p><p><em>Keep an eye out for episode 2 of Stab In The Dark. There’s SO much more to come…</em></p>",
